                     <note>Calendar (fol. 1), Proprium de Tempore (fol. 7), Psalter with canticles, etc. (fol. 187), 'Hymni tam dominicales quam festiui' (fol. 244v), Proprium ('festiuitates') Sanctorum, with minor offices (foL 267).</note>
