                     <decoNote type="decInit">Fine initials. By <persName key="person_96179506" role="art">Frate Nebridio</persName>. (<ref target="https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/000468709">Pächt and Alexander</ref> ii. 735, pl. LXXI)</decoNote>
